statement: SELECT  count(*) FROM   PhotoObj p  join ZooNoSpec z on p.objID = z.objID  join SpecObj s on p.objID = s.bestobjID WHERE  s.class = 'Galaxy' and  s.z < 0.01
SELECT  count(*) FROM   PhotoObj p  join ZooNoSpec z on p.objID = z.objID  join SpecObj s on p.objID = s.bestobjID WHERE s.z < 0.01 and s.class = 'Test'
SELECT  count(*) FROM   Galaxy g  join ZooNoSpec z on g.objID = z.objID  join SpecObj s on g.objID = s.bestobjID WHERE  s.z < 0.01
SELECT count(*) FROM GalaxyTag gt JOIN Photoz pz ON pz.objID=gt.objID WHERE gt.ra BETWEEN 150 AND 151 AND gt.dec BETWEEN 29.5 AND 30.6556 AND pz.nnvol<0.45 AND pz.photoerrorclass=1 AND pz.zerr<0.03
select count(s.z) FROM photoObj p JOIN specObj s ON s.bestObjID = p.objID JOIN plateX x ON x.plateID = s.plateID  where p.type=3 and s.zwarning=0 and s.class='galaxy' and s.z between -0.5 and 0

SELECT   p.run, p.camcol, p.field, count(s.z) as count, avg(s.z) as average  FROM photoObj p  JOIN specObj s ON s.bestObjID = p.objID  WHERE   s.class = 'galaxy'  and p.run = 5112   and camcol = 1   GROUP BY   p.run,p.camcol,p.field  ORDER BY  avg(s.z) desc

select  p.field, avg(s.z), count(s.z) from  PhotoObj p join SpecObj s on p.objID = s.bestObjID where s.class='galaxy' and p.run=5112 and p.camcol=1 group by p.run, p.camcol, p.field order by avg(s.z) desc
select  p.field, avg(s.z) from  PhotoObj p join SpecObj s on p.objID = s.bestObjID where s.class='galaxy' and p.run=5112 and p.camcol=1 group by p.run, p.camcol, p.field order by avg(s.z) desc

SELECT  count(*) as count FROM   PhotoObj p  join ZooSpec z on p.objID = z.objID  join SpecObj s on p.objID = s.bestobjID  join Galaxy g on g.objID = p.objID WHERE  s.class = 'Galaxy'  and z.p_el > 0.8  and s.z < 0.05

SELECT  count(*) as count, avg(p.u) as u, avg(p.g) as g, avg(p.r) as r, avg(p.i) as i, avg(p.z) as z, avg(p.u-p.r) as ur, avg(g.petroRad_g) as Rad, avg(g.petroR50_g) as R50, avg(g.petroR90_g) as R90, avg(s.z) FROM   PhotoObj p  join ZooSpec z on p.objID = z.objID  join SpecObj s on p.objID = s.bestobjID  join Galaxy g on g.objID = p.objID WHERE  s.class = 'Galaxy'  and z.p_cs > 0.8

select count(*) FROM PhotoObj AS p  JOIN SpecObj AS s ON s.bestobjid = p.objid WHERE   s.class = 'GALAXY'   AND p.r > 18 and p.r < 20  AND p.petrorad_r < 2  AND p.r <= 2.5   AND p.i >= -0.2   AND p.r-p.z <= 0.5 and p.u-p.r >= 2.5*(p.r-p.z) and p.g-p.r-p.r >= 0.5-p.i
SELECT COUNT(p.objid) as CNT FROM PhotoObjAll AS p JOIN SpecObjAll s ON p.objID = s.bestObjID WHERE p.dec >= 52 and p.dec < 60

SELECT s.class, count(*) as numEvents FROM PhotoObj AS p JOIN SpecObj AS s on p.objid = s.bestobjid WHERE p.type = 3   AND s.z < 0.1 GROUP BY s.class HAVING count(*) > 2000 ORDER BY numEvents limit 10

SELECT count(*) as total, sum( case when (Type=3) then 1 else 0 end) as Galaxies  FROM PhotoObj AS p  JOIN SpecObj AS s ON s.bestobjid = p.objid  JOIN GalSpecLine AS L ON s.SpecObjID = L.SpecObjID WHERE   ((S.class = 'GALAXY' and S. subclass = 'AGN') and S.class = 'QSO') and   SNmedian > 10 and (S.z BETWEEN 0.02 and 0.35) and S.zwarning = 0
select P.objID, count(P.objID) From PhotoObjAll P JOIN Neighbors AS N ON P.objid = N.ObjID JOIN PhotoObjAll AS L ON L.objid = N.NeighborObjID GROUP BY P.objID  limit 1
select P.objID, count(P.objID) From PhotoObjAll P JOIN Neighbors AS N ON P.objid = N.ObjID JOIN PhotoObjAll AS L ON L.objid = N.NeighborObjID GROUP BY P.objID  limit 100
select P.objID From PhotoObjAll P JOIN Neighbors AS N ON P.objid = N.ObjID JOIN PhotoObjAll AS L ON L.objid = N.NeighborObjID GROUP BY P.objID  limit 100

SELECT count(*) FROM mangaPipe3D p LEFT JOIN (  SELECT r.*  ,'manga-' + r.plateifu as manganame   FROM mangaDRPall r  ) t on t.manganame = p.mangaID WHERE p.log_Mass_gas != -12  AND p.e_log_Mass_gas != -9999  AND t.nsa_sersic_n > 3  AND t.nsa_sersic_n < 6

SELECT count(*) FROM mangaPipe3D p LEFT JOIN (  SELECT r.*  ,'manga-' + r.plateifu as manganame   FROM mangaDRPall r  ) t on t.manganame = p.mangaID WHERE p.log_Mass_gas != -12  AND p.e_log_Mass_gas != -9999  AND t.nsa_sersic_n = 6

SELECT count(*) FROM mangaPipe3D p LEFT JOIN (  SELECT r.*  ,'manga-' + r.plateifu as manganame   FROM mangaDRPall r  ) t on t.manganame = p.mangaID WHERE p.log_Mass_gas != -12  AND p.e_log_Mass_gas != -9999  AND t.nsa_sersic_n < 3

SELECT count(*) FROM mangaPipe3D p LEFT JOIN (  SELECT r.*  ,'manga-' + r.plateifu as manganame   FROM mangaDRPall r  ) t on t.manganame = p.mangaID WHERE p.log_Mass_gas != -12  AND p.e_log_Mass_gas != -9999  AND t.nsa_sersic_n > 3

SELECT count(*) FROM mangaPipe3D p LEFT JOIN (  SELECT r.*  ,'manga-' + r.plateifu as manganame   FROM mangaDRPall r  ) t on t.manganame = p.mangaID WHERE p.log_Mass_gas != -12  AND p.e_log_Mass_gas != -9999

SELECT p.mangaID FROM mangaPipe3D p LEFT JOIN (  SELECT r.*  ,'manga-' + r.plateifu as manganame   FROM mangaDRPall r  ) t on t.manganame = p.mangaID WHERE p.log_Mass_gas != -12  AND p.e_log_Mass_gas != -9999  AND t.nsa_sersic_n < 3 group by p.mangaID
select count(distinct spp.specobjid) from photoobjall as p  JOIN spplines as spp on spp.bestobjid = p.objid  WHERE   p.ra between 125 and 129 and p.dec between 5 and 9

select count(distinct s.specobjid) from photoobjall as p  JOIN specobjall as s on s.bestobjid = p.objid OR s.fluxobjid = p.objid OR s.targetobjid = p.objid WHERE   p.ra between 125 and 129 and p.dec between 5 and 9

SELECT p.objid ,min(abs(ns.zdist - 0.134906)) ,min(abs(p.ra - 122.077051)) ,min(abs(p.dec - 49.633482)) from PhotoObj AS p  JOIN SpecObj AS s ON s.bestobjid = p.objid  JOIN nsatlas AS ns ON ns.z = s.z  and s.class = 'GALAXY'  and p.z > 0  group by p.objid limit 10

SELECT p.objid ,min(abs(ns.zdist - 0.134906)) ,min(abs(p.ra - 122.077051)) ,min(abs(p.dec - 49.633482)) from PhotoObj AS p  JOIN SpecObj AS s ON s.bestobjid = p.objid  JOIN nsatlas AS ns ON ns.z = s.z  and s.class = 'GALAXY'  and p.z > 0  group by p.objid limit 10

SELECT COUNT(p.objid) AS Ct, MAX(p.psfMag_z) AS Mag,  cast((p.ra/cos(cast(p.dec/5 as int)*5.0))/5 as int)*5.0 as raCosDec,  cast(p.dec/5 as int)*5.0 as dec FROM PhotoTag AS p  INNER JOIN  (SELECT MIN(q.psfMag_z) AS MZ,  cast((ra/cos(cast(dec/5 as int)*5.0))/5 as int)*5.0 as raCosDec,  cast(dec/5 as int)*5.0 as dec  FROM PhotoTag as q WHERE   (q.dec BETWEEN 70 AND 75) AND  (q.type = 6) AND  (q.psfMag_z > -9999)  GROUP BY cast((ra/cos(cast(dec/5 as int)*5.0))/5 as int)*5.0,  cast(dec/5 as int)*5.0   ) AS p1 ON p1.raCosDec=(cast((p.ra/cos(cast(p.dec/5 as int)*5.0))/5 as int)*5.0) AND p1.dec = (cast(p.dec/5 as int)*5.0) WHERE   (p.dec BETWEEN 70 AND 75) AND  (p.type = 6) AND  (p.psfMag_z < p1.MZ+1) GROUP BY cast((p.ra/cos(cast(p.dec/5 as int)*5.0))/5 as int)*5.0,  cast(p.dec/5 as int)*5.0  ORDER BY cast((p.ra/cos(cast(p.dec/5 as int)*5.0))/5 as int)*5.0

SELECT  p.objID, s.specObjID, mp3d.mangaID, mtar.mangaID,  pcam.mstellar_median AS mMass, pcam.mstellar_err AS mMerr,  mp3d.log_Mass AS mpMass, mp3d.e_log_Mass AS mpMerr,  mp3d.log_Mass_gas AS mpMassGas, mp3d.e_log_Mass_gas AS mpMGerr,  pcam.vdisp_median AS mVD, pcam.vdisp_err AS mVDerr,  p.devRad_r, p.devRadErr_r, mp3d.re_arc, mp3d.re_kpc,  mp3d.redshift AS mp_z, s.z AS Sredshift, pz.z AS Predshift, s.zErr AS SredshiftErr,  nsa.sersic_n,  nsa.sersic_absmag_r AS AbsMag_r,  nsa.sersic_ba, mp3d.ellip,   g.specsfr_tot_p50 AS specSFR, g.sfr_tot_p50 AS SFR,  COUNT(*) as CNT FROM mangaPipe3D as mp3d  JOIN mangaDAPall as mdap on mdap.objra = mp3d.objra AND mdap.objdec = mp3d.objdec  JOIN mangatarget as mtar on mtar.mangaID = mtar.mangaID  JOIN nsatlas as nsa on nsa.nsaid = mtar.nsa_nsaid  JOIN SpecObjAll as s on s.z = nsa.z  JOIN stellarMassPCAWiscM11 as pcam on pcam.specObjID = s.specObjID  JOIN photoz as pz on pz.objID = s.bestObjID  JOIN zooSpec as z on z.specobjid = s.specObjID  JOIN galSpecExtra as g on g.specObjID = s.specObjID  JOIN PhotoObjAll as p on p.objID = s.bestObjID WHERE   s.z BETWEEN 0.00 AND 0.15  AND p.devRadErr_r BETWEEN 0.00000000000000000001 AND 100  AND p.devRad_r > 0  AND p.fracDev_r > 0.9  AND Z.p_cs_debiased <= 0.3  AND z.elliptical = 1  AND s.class = 'galaxy'  AND nsa.sersic_ba > 0.85  AND s.velDisp > 0  AND pcam.vdisp_median > 0  AND pcam.mstellar_median >= 10.4  AND pcam.warning = 0  AND g.specsfr_tot_p50 > -9999  AND g.sfr_tot_p50 > -9999  AND nsa.sersic_n BETWEEN 3 AND 5.5  AND nsa.sersic_absmag_r > -23  AND mp3d.log_Mass_gas > 0  AND mp3d.e_log_Mass_gas > 0 GROUP BY  p.objID, s.specObjID, mp3d.mangaID, mtar.mangaID,  pcam.mstellar_median, pcam.mstellar_err,  mp3d.log_Mass, mp3d.e_log_Mass,  mp3d.log_Mass_gas, mp3d.e_log_Mass_gas,  pcam.vdisp_median, pcam.vdisp_err,  p.devRad_r, p.devRadErr_r, mp3d.re_arc, mp3d.re_kpc,  mp3d.redshift, s.z, pz.z, s.zErr,  nsa.sersic_n,  nsa.sersic_absmag_r,  nsa.sersic_ba, mp3d.ellip,   g.specsfr_tot_p50, g.sfr_tot_p50 HAVING COUNT (*) > 1 limit 500000

SELECT  p.objID, s.specObjID, mp3d.mangaID, mtar.mangaID,  pcam.mstellar_median AS mMass, pcam.mstellar_err AS mMerr,  mp3d.log_Mass AS mpMass, mp3d.e_log_Mass AS mpMerr,  mp3d.log_Mass_gas AS mpMassGas, mp3d.e_log_Mass_gas AS mpMGerr,  pcam.vdisp_median AS mVD, pcam.vdisp_err AS mVDerr,  p.devRad_r, p.devRadErr_r, mp3d.re_arc, mp3d.re_kpc,  mp3d.redshift AS mp_z, s.z AS Sredshift, pz.z AS Predshift, s.zErr AS SredshiftErr,  nsa.sersic_n,  nsa.sersic_absmag_r AS AbsMag_r,  nsa.sersic_ba, mp3d.ellip,   g.specsfr_tot_p50 AS specSFR, g.sfr_tot_p50 AS SFR,  COUNT(*) as CNT FROM mangaPipe3D as mp3d  JOIN mangaDAPall as mdap on mdap.objra = mp3d.objra AND mdap.objdec = mp3d.objdec  JOIN mangatarget as mtar on mtar.mangaID = mtar.mangaID  JOIN nsatlas as nsa on nsa.nsaid = mtar.nsa_nsaid  JOIN SpecObjAll as s on s.z = nsa.z  JOIN stellarMassPCAWiscM11 as pcam on pcam.specObjID = s.specObjID  JOIN photoz as pz on pz.objID = s.bestObjID  JOIN zooSpec as z on z.specobjid = s.specObjID  JOIN galSpecExtra as g on g.specObjID = s.specObjID  JOIN PhotoObjAll as p on p.objID = s.bestObjID WHERE   s.z BETWEEN 0.00 AND 0.15  AND p.devRadErr_r BETWEEN 0.00000000000000000001 AND 100  AND p.devRad_r > 0  AND p.fracDev_r > 0.9  AND Z.p_cs_debiased <= 0.3  AND z.elliptical = 1  AND s.class = 'galaxy'  AND nsa.sersic_ba > 0.85  AND s.velDisp > 0  AND pcam.vdisp_median > 0  AND pcam.mstellar_median >= 10.4  AND pcam.warning = 0  AND g.specsfr_tot_p50 > -9999  AND g.sfr_tot_p50 > -9999  AND nsa.sersic_n BETWEEN 3 AND 5.5  AND nsa.sersic_absmag_r > -23  AND mp3d.log_Mass_gas > 0  AND mp3d.e_log_Mass_gas > 0 GROUP BY  p.objID, s.specObjID, mp3d.mangaID, mtar.mangaID,  pcam.mstellar_median, pcam.mstellar_err,  mp3d.log_Mass, mp3d.e_log_Mass,  mp3d.log_Mass_gas, mp3d.e_log_Mass_gas,  pcam.vdisp_median, pcam.vdisp_err,  p.devRad_r, p.devRadErr_r, mp3d.re_arc, mp3d.re_kpc,  mp3d.redshift, s.z, pz.z, s.zErr,  nsa.sersic_n,  nsa.sersic_absmag_r,  nsa.sersic_ba, mp3d.ellip,   g.specsfr_tot_p50, g.sfr_tot_p50 HAVING COUNT (*) > 1 limit 2000

select count(*) from ( SELECT sl.specobjid, sp.spectypesubclass, sp.teffadop, sp.flag from sppLINES as sl  JOIN sppParams AS sp ON sl.specobjid = sp.specobjid  ) as spp left outer join ( select specObjID, class, subClass, ra, dec from specObjAll ) as spec on spp.specobjid=spec.specObjid where spec.class = 'star'  and spectypesubclass = 'SKY'

select count(*) from ( SELECT sl.specobjid, sp.spectypesubclass, sp.teffadop, sp.flag from sppLINES as sl  JOIN sppParams AS sp ON sl.specobjid = sp.specobjid  ) as spp left outer join ( select specObjID, class, subClass, ra, dec from specObj ) as spec on spp.specobjid=spec.specObjid where spec.class = 'star'  and spectypesubclass = 'SKY'
select count(*) FROM PhotoObj AS p join specobj as s on s.bestobjid = p.objid or s.fluxObjID = p.objid or s.targetobjid = p.objid WHERE   p.l BETWEEN 217 AND 218  AND p.b BETWEEN 23 AND 25

SELECT x.class, (1.0 * x.numEvents / x.allEvents) as ratio FROM (  SELECT v1.class, v1.numEvents, (  SELECT count(*) as allEvents  FROM PhotoObj AS p  JOIN SpecObj AS s on p.objid = s.bestobjid  WHERE p.type = 3   AND s.z < 0.1  ) AS allEvents  FROM (  SELECT s.class, count(*) as numEvents  FROM PhotoObj AS p  JOIN SpecObj AS s on p.objid = s.bestobjid  WHERE p.type = 3   AND s.z < 0.1  GROUP BY s.class  ) AS v1 ) AS x

SELECT x.class, (x.numEvents / x.allEvents) as ratio FROM (  SELECT v1.class, v1.numEvents, (  SELECT count(*) as allEvents  FROM PhotoObj AS p  JOIN SpecObj AS s on p.objid = s.bestobjid  WHERE p.type = 3   AND s.z < 0.1  ) AS allEvents  FROM (  SELECT s.class, count(*) as numEvents  FROM PhotoObj AS p  JOIN SpecObj AS s on p.objid = s.bestobjid  WHERE p.type = 3   AND s.z < 0.1  GROUP BY s.class  ) AS v1 ) AS x
